extends ../../layouts/_layout-en.pug

block vars
  - var title = 'ZT Code Craft | PartDepot'
  - var assetPath = '../../'
  - var altLangUrl = '/bg/portfolio/partdepot.html'

block extraStyles
  link(rel='stylesheet' media='screen' href='../../assets/vendor/aos/dist/aos.css')
  link(rel='stylesheet' media='screen' href='../../assets/vendor/swiper/swiper-bundle.min.css')

block content
  //- Hero
  section.position-relative.mb-5
    .bg-secondary.position-absolute.top-0.end-0.w-50.h-100.d-none.d-lg-block
    .bg-secondary.position-absolute.top-0.end-0.w-100.h-100.d-lg-none
    .container.position-relative.zindex-2.py-5.pb-lg-0
      nav(aria-label='breadcrumb')
        ol.pt-lg-2.pb-1.breadcrumb
          li.breadcrumb-item: a(href='/index.html') Home
          li.breadcrumb-item: a(href='/en/portfolio.html') Portfolio
          li.breadcrumb-item.active(aria-current='page') PArtDepot
      .d-lg-flex.align-items-center.pt-3.pb-xxl-5
        img.d-block.order-lg-2.me-auto.me-lg-0.ms-auto(src='../../assets/img/portfolio/partdepot/part-transp.png' width='480' alt='Image')
        .order-lg-1.text-center.text-lg-start.pe-lg-4.py-4.py-md-5
          h1.display-2.text-uppercase.pb-3.pb-lg-4 Crafting a Dynamic Digital Canvas
          p.fs-lg.mx-auto.mx-lg-0.mb-0(style='max-width: 530px;') Elevating PartDepot's Brand: From Custom Design Integration to Dynamic Content Management with Contentful.
      ul.nav.justify-content-center.justify-content-lg-start.mx-n2.pt-lg-5.mb-0
        li.nav-item.me-3: a.nav-link.p-2(href='https://www.instagram.com/p_artdepot/' target='_blank') Instagram
        li.nav-item.me-3: a.nav-link.p-2(href='https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=100092269797665' target='_blank') Facebook

  //- Content
  section.container.overflow-hidden.pt-lg-2.pt-xl-4.pt-xxl-5
    .row.py-sm-3.py-md-4.py-lg-5
      //- Sticky sidebar
      .col-md-3.col-lg-2
        .d-flex.d-md-block.flex-wrap.position-sticky.top-0
          .pb-3.mb-2.mb-lg-4.me-5.me-md-0
            h2.fs-base.fw-normal.text-muted.mb-2 Company
            ul.list-unstyled.fs-lg.fw-semibold.text-dark.mb-0
              li.d-block.py-1 PArtDepot
              li.d-block.py-1 5-10 employees
              li.d-block.py-1 Burgas, Bulgaria
              li.d-block.py-1: a.text-dark(href='https://ztcodecraft.github.io/PArtDepot/' target='_blank') Visit website
          .pb-3.mb-2.mb-lg-4.me-5.me-md-0
            h2.fs-base.fw-normal.text-muted.mb-2 Indusrty
            ul.list-unstyled.fs-lg.fw-semibold.text-dark.mb-0
              li.d-block.py-1 Arts and Entertainment
          .pb-3.mb-2.mb-lg-4.me-5.me-md-0
            h2.fs-base.fw-normal.text-muted.mb-2 Services
            ul.list-unstyled.fs-lg.fw-semibold.text-dark.mb-0
              li.d-block.py-1 Web Development
              li.d-block.py-1 Dynamic Custom Content
          .pb-3.mb-2.mb-lg-4
            h2.fs-base.fw-normal.text-muted.mb-2 Time spent
            ul.list-unstyled.fs-lg.fw-semibold.text-dark.mb-0
              li.d-block.py-1 2023, 1-2 months

      //- Description
      .col-md-9.offset-lg-1
        .ps-md-4.ps-lg-0
          .border-bottom.pb-3.pb-sm-4.pb-lg-5.mb-4
            p.text-dark.lead.mb-md-2.mb-lg-3.mb-xl-4 Discover how we revamped PartDepot's online presence, seamlessly integrating their unique branding and enabling dynamic schedule updates through Contentful. Uncover the details of our creative collaboration.
          h2.h1.pt-2.pt-sm-3.pt-md-4.pt-lg-5.pb-2 About the client
          p.fs-lg PartDepot is an <b>art studio and cultural hub</b> committed to unlocking the potential of individuals through art and physical activities. With a diverse range of activities, including yoga, art therapy, and cardio workouts, PartDepot creates outstanding conditions for personal growth. The studio is also available for rent to various art organizations, contributing to cultural and educational endeavours. Harmony and balance of the spirit and body form the core of PartDepot's philosophy, guiding their approach to physical and emotional development.
          h2.h1.pt-3.pt-sm-4.pt-xl-5.pb-2 The challenge
          p.fs-lg PartDepot, an art studio with a vibrant vision, faced the challenge of translating their energetic brand identity into an engaging online presence. With pre-existing branding colors and unique custom fonts, maintaining consistency while infusing these elements into a functional and visually appealing website was a key challenge. Additionally, the need for a dynamic feature—allowing seamless schedule updates for their diverse range of activities—required a tailored solution to empower PartDepot with easy content management.
          h2.h1.pt-3.pt-sm-4.pt-xl-5.pb-2 The solution
          p.fs-lg.mb-0 We crafted a website that captures the essence of their energetic brand. Leveraging their existing branding colors and preferred custom fonts, we ensured a cohesive and visually stimulating design. Customized illustrations were seamlessly integrated to further enhance the website's uniqueness. To address the need for dynamic content management, we implemented a solution using the Contentful platform. Now, PartDepot has full control over their class schedule, empowering them to make real-time updates easily. The result is a vibrant, user-friendly website that not only reflects PartDepot's artistic spirit but also provides practical tools for effective online engagement.

    //- Images
    .position-relative.w-100.mx-auto.pb-4.pb-sm-3.pb-md-4(style='max-width: 1043px;')
      img.d-block.position-relative.zindex-5(src='../../assets/img/portfolio/partdepot/2.png' alt='Image' data-aos='fade-down-right' data-aos-duration='1500' data-aos-offset='250')
      img.d-block.position-absolute.top-0.start-0(src='../../assets/img/portfolio/partdepot/3.png' alt='Image' data-aos='zoom-in' data-aos-duration='1200' data-aos-offset='250')
      img.d-block.position-absolute.top-0.start-0.zindex-1(src='../../assets/img/portfolio/partdepot/4.png' alt='Image' data-aos='fade-down' data-aos-duration='800' data-aos-offset='250')
      img.d-block.d-dark-mode-none.position-absolute.top-0.start-0.zindex-2(src='../../assets/img/portfolio/partdepot/5.png' alt='Image' data-aos='fade-left' data-aos-duration='1200' data-aos-offset='250')
      img.d-none.d-dark-mode-block(src='' width='')

    //- Results
    .row.pt-1.pt-sm-3.pt-md-4.pb-5.mb-md-2.mb-lg-3.mb-xl-4.mb-xxl-5
      .col-md-11.col-lg-9.col-xl-8.pb-1.pb-sm-3.pb-md-4
        h2.h1.pb-sm-2.pb-lg-3 Results
        p.fs-lg.mb-0 The project resulted in a <b>responsive and user-friendly website</b> that authentically mirrors PartDepot's artistic spirit. Now equipped with seamless <b>schedule management</b>, they can efficiently engage with their community through clear and dynamic updates.

  //- Parallax background image
  section.jarallax(data-jarallax data-speed='0.6')
    .ratio.ratio-16x9
    .jarallax-img(style='background-image: url(../../assets/img/portfolio/partdepot/mockups.png);')

  //- Testimonials
  section.container.position-relative.zindex-2.py-5.mt-n1.mt-sm-0.mb-1.my-md-3.my-lg-3.my-xl-4.my-xxl-5
    .row.py-md-4.py-lg-5
      .col-md-9.col-lg-7.order-md-2
        .swiper(data-swiper-options='{"spaceBetween":40,"loop":true,"bindedContent":true,"autoHeight":true,"pagination":{"el":".testimonials-count","type":"fraction"},"navigation":{"prevEl":"#prev-testimonial","nextEl":"#next-testimonial"}}')
          div
            div
              .d-flex.d-md-none.pt-3.mb-3
                i.ai-quotes.d-md-none.text-primary.display-3.mt-n2
                .ps-3
                  h3.h5.mb-0 Pamela Trifonova
                  p.text-muted.mb-0 Owner of PartDepot
              h2.mb-lg-4 Great work and attitude!
              p.lead.mb-0 Work on the website was fully tailored to the time I had available, remote online meetings were key to shaping the vision and concept. The process was extremely easy and pleasant, bearing in mind my information illiteracy at times, the team was extremely patient and guided me in detail through the individual stages in the design and development of the site. They assisted me with the visual elements and design, as well as choosing a suitable domain. I would definitely recommend them to my friends starting their businesses.
      .col-md-3.offset-lg-1.order-md-1.mt-n3
        i.ai-quotes.d-none.d-md-block.text-primary.ms-n2.mb-1(style='font-size: 150px;')
        .binded-content.h-auto.d-none.d-md-block
          .binded-item.h-auto.active#testimonial-1
            h3.h5.mb-1 Pamela Trifonova
            p.text-muted.mb-0 Owner of PartDepot

  //- Next projects
  section.container.pb-5.mb-2.mb-lg-3.mb-xl-4.mb-xxl-5
    h2.h1.pb-3.pb-lg-4 Next projects
    .row.row-cols-1.row-cols-sm-2.align-items-end.mb-2.pb-md-4
      .col
        .zoom-effect.position-relative.border-bottom.pb-3(style='max-width: 550px;')
          .zoom-effect-wrapper
            .zoom-effect-img: img(src='../../assets/img/portfolio/magenta/grid.png' alt='Image')
          .pt-4.mt-lg-2
            h2.h4.mb-2: a.stretched-link(href='magenta-zine.html') Magenta Zine
            .d-flex.justify-content-between.fs-lg.text-muted
              span Web Development, Blog, Branding
              span 2023

block extraScripts
  script(src='../../assets/vendor/aos/dist/aos.js')
  script(src='../../assets/vendor/jarallax/dist/jarallax.min.js')
  script(src='../../assets/vendor/swiper/swiper-bundle.min.js')
